PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774620679
OL,3,CWoman to lead Red Arrows for first
OL,4,Ctime at English Riviera Airshow
OL,6,FThe experienced fast-jet pilot, who
OL,7,Fjoined the Royal Air Force in 2005,
OL,8,Ftook charge of the 150-strong unit at
OL,9,Fthe start of the year and oversee all
OL,10,Faspects of the Red Arrows. This will
OL,11,Fbe one of her first public appearances
OL,12,Fin the role.
OL,14,FShe has previously told ITV News: "I'm
OL,15,Fincredibly proud and excited to be
OL,16,Fcommanding a team whose aim is to
OL,17,Frepresent the UK and help inspire
OL,18,Ffuture generations of aviators from
OL,19,Fall backgrounds.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774620679
OL,3,CWoman to lead Red Arrows for first
OL,4,Ctime at English Riviera Airshow
OL,6,F"This is a great time to be joining
OL,7,Fthe Red Arrows, as we prepare for a
OL,8,Fbusy season and plan for the future.
OL,10,F"I can't wait to work alongside team
OL,11,Fmembers and have the opportunity to
OL,12,Fmeet people at airshows and events
OL,13,Fthis year."
OL,15,FThe three day event is the 10th
OL,16,FEnglish Riviera Airshow and takes
OL,17,Fplace in Paignton.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
