PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774620679
OL,3,CWoman to lead Red Arrows for first
OL,4,Ctime at English Riviera Airshow
OL,6,FThe show is put together by Torbay
OL,7,FCouncil, the English Riviera BID
OL,8,FCompany, local businesses and aviation
OL,9,Fenthusiasts.
OL,11,FBesides the Red Arrows this year's
OL,12,Fevent also stars the Typhoon and
OL,13,FBattle of Britain Memorial Flight.
OL,15,FCllr Jackie Thomas, Torbay Council
OL,16,FCabinet Member for Tourism, Culture &
OL,17,FEvents, and Corporate Services,
OL,18,Fexplained how this year's line up will
OL,19,Fbe 'truly unforgettable.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
