PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1774620679
OL,3,CWoman to lead Red Arrows for first
OL,4,Ctime at English Riviera Airshow
OL,6,FShe said: "This is a fantastic
OL,7,Fopportunity for visitors to experience
OL,8,Fthe power, precision and heritage of
OL,9,Fthe RAF's most iconic display teams,
OL,10,Fand we can't wait to welcome everyone
OL,11,Ffor what promises to be a spectacular
OL,12,Fcelebration."
